summary: A saved game of a level 1 girl named Emilie.
descriptionHtml:
Download instructions:
Download the file and open the saved game. Depending on the saved game you choose you might need alternative start, otherwise your character will start out in a random place in skyrim.
Load the save, use shadowracemenu and then press F5 to save the face, after that press F9 to apply it.
Tip: Only use for ningheim for it to work properly.
Required:
Sevenbase body replacer. Ningheim race. Coverwomen.  SG female eyebrows. SG female textures renewal. Apachii sky hair. (Leave a comment if the saved game doesn't work.
author: Mugiwara
